==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cutthroat
<hw>Cut"throat`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Murderous; cruel;
barbarous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Ruthless; conducted without restraint; <as>as,
